    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Guidance for full opening: special schools and other specialist settings
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What all special schools and other specialist settings will need to do during the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak from the start of the autumn term to support the return of children and young people with special education needs and disability (SEND).</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
